{"tid":1468752,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥助攻《以退為進，定下死線》","createTime":"2019-08-13T20:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:54.000Z","uid":79957,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"62b96482cb411fb96818ae04e9e93e76560ead9a","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:34:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有小小長，但請大家睇曬佢，認真考慮以下建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n自從71勇武升級，衝過立法會後<br />\n和理非跟住一齊升級，搞過大大小小嘅不合作運動<br />\n但對方無視一切道德，繼續不斷暴力鎮壓我地<br />\n<br />\n去到今日<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我方有數之不盡嘅人命傷亡，接近千名同伴被捕</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n同時間更有大量有心人不斷製造風向<br />\n企圖將我地抺黑為撕裂社會嘅一份子，甚至係始作俑者<br />\n<br />\n經歷過812嘅白色恐佈<br />\n大家更係進退失據<br />\n係打算用王牌佔領機場嘅同時<br />\n<strong>法庭已批出清場手令俾警犬合法清場</strong><br />\n任何機場和平示威均會自動跌入法網<br />\n<br />\n係呢個迷失關頭<br />\n林鄭竟然係記者會上<br />\n將無法修補社會怪罪落我地到<br />\n佢話，一切修補要等社會平靜返落嚟先做<br />\n<br />\n心水清嘅大家應該睇得出<br />\n林鄭係行左好關鍵嘅一步<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過係錯得好關鍵嘅一步</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直頭係交撚左助攻俾我地！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佢咁講係因為好有信心我地會繼續搞事<br />\n但如果萬一嚟緊嘅日子咩事都冇發生，佢仲有咩藉口？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以在此，我呼籲大家<br />\n<strong>816攬炒巴集會</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>照去！</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong>818民陣遊行</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">照去！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n然後以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月18日 星期日</span></span></strong>呢一日為起點<br />\n<strong>之後一個星期內我地停止所有和理非 勇武行動</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一、俾喘息空間我地每一位，不論係打生打死嘅勇武兄弟，或者默默守護嘅和理非手足<br />\n<br />\n二、製造一個星期嘅絕對平靜，要林鄭無從迴避，必須正面回應訴求<br />\n<br />\n三、重建形象，俾香港大眾抖抖，贏返民心之餘，話俾全世界知我地除左向前衝，更識得以退為進，依然係文明高質嘅香港人<br />\n</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一星期後，8月25日</span></span></strong><br />\n如果林鄭政府依舊唔講人話<br />\n警察繼續進行大追捕<br />\n律政司不斷起訴我地嘅兄弟<br />\n<br />\n就正式宣佈大三罷<br />\n罷課 罷買 罷市<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>同埋，<br />\n我地街頭再見</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb640a2c5cd1aa6c7882e798c0b07cc3e94e8ac","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:36:24.000Z","msg":"第一次出長文建議<br />\n文字上會有講得唔好嘅地方，歡迎大家糾正，加入討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6633973f1714d76deea701c437eee4ec7454cf0","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:36:45.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6d79ae7c12fb3764609baa6422ec426356286a24","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:37:03.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e5f60c896590a6b4b62b48fe2a69dbdd80df6e0f","tid":1468752,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:37:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，好忙無睇直播，昨晚發生乜事，嚴重過811 少女比警察開槍打爆左隻眼？？"},{"pid":"1406debbd8e8f8a67fa41b807379e0febe49dc6c","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5f60c896590a6b4b62b48fe2a69dbdd80df6e0f","tid":1468752,"uid":230703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:37:05.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，好忙無睇直播，昨晚發生乜事，嚴重過811 少女比警察開槍打爆左隻眼？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:43:44.000Z","msg":"如果你係問緊812，<br />\n就係出現左6月至今最嚴重嘅白色恐佈<br />\n大批和平、手無寸鐵嘅市民，擔心係機場被鎮壓甚至屠殺，徒步由機場逃出東涌<br />\n<br />\n如果係問813<br />\n就係發生左6月至今最嚴重嘅不信任情況<br />\n因為警方擺左好多卧底係示威人群，導致彼此間極不信任，更引致連登部份人打破「不割蓆」嘅諾言<br />\n<br />\n所以我提出以退為進<br />\n好多巴打問點樣捉鬼<br />\n好簡單，冇人聚集，就唔會俾鬼有機可乘"},{"pid":"b7f37fefa1ff1835addbee87df6610bc4c745124","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:44:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3502c9c8116ded8fde226475bda34dd3ec260ac9","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:44:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5c0019778447789e6d2ead0aeeeeb80a75fc63cf","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:46:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c1f7534cb374ab1dfbe13de65f69cc6455b95c86","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:46:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"16993e8689f0e86f80367ce2975331f78bf9dac2","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:47:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b7cb117837f7d738f1d1696632dfb5317efe5648","tid":1468752,"uid":272892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:49:18.000Z","msg":"香港人加油！永不放棄！"},{"pid":"2b591ebe2f8f33fca879744a2a8c2d8c16facacc","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T23:44:05.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9f395a10d0ca1467def1334e2e8bf095bd782dab","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ecff4d75156bec8356d022e189819f5bea905a4","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:52:47.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係正負皮啦，一齊討論下可行性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f54a0e0ffc9fbd3621ca88c3c6ae1d0f65a553","tid":1468752,"uid":2625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:01:22.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"4bf602bd64e9be1702b006a8b007bdf8e708bde1","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:02:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"10b6677c9d8c8de0932fba0deffb296cff6787b7","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:02:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"22b4045f5f875f9256e8e10d7f5aaa4bfc797cec","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ceaa98027030e8372d858d094c9d62b63e66e36","tid":1468752,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}